hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: very best job kopa kavana A shotgun is not an assault weapon, even though there is no such thing anyways. That did not keep this guy from killing 12 people with a firearm that only holds "five" shells. That is not high capacity, which again proves that capacity of a firearm means nothing. You have to insert new shells one at a time, and yet, no one could stop him while he did it. Just as limiting an AR-15 to 15 rounds would do nothing against a person motivated to kill as many people as they could.
